# CODEOWNERS for offshore-vault
#
# Paths listed below require @brunobueno95 review before a PR can merge.
# The agent pipeline's auto-merge is intentionally blocked on any PR that
# touches these paths, because an autonomous agent should never change the
# rules, the schema, the validator, the tooling, or the CI configuration.
#
# Article content files under drilling/, crane-and-logistics/, subsea/, and
# emergency-response/ are NOT listed here. Those are the paths bot PRs are
# allowed to touch and auto-merge when CI is green.
#
# Validator-written files (_UNRESOLVED_LINKS.md, _VALIDATION_REPORT.md,
# _TODO_QUEUE.md, _MANIFEST.txt, _PIPELINE_REPORT.md) are also NOT listed,
# because the pipeline writes them every run.

